{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"dae93cd912","title":"周恩来接见广州造反派和解放军报记者","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"36694bf057","index":0,"year":1967,"month":8,"day":24,"articleId":"dae93cd912","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"周恩来","id":"523bb79e8f","type":"人物"},{"name":"军队和军事","id":"6f7a683373","type":"主题"},{"name":"关键人物文稿","id":"c20d333791","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"文章","id":"c9f57d6426","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"造反运动和派别斗争","id":"d48f0ea3e8","type":"主题"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"81fa500bdd","type":"title","text":"周恩来接见广州造反派和解放军报记者","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"dae93cd912","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7ddfec34b2","type":"paragraph","text":"24日晨，总理单独接见了广州“红旗工人”、中南局联络总部和解放军报记者各一人，谈话主要精神：","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"dae93cd912","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"341cd64e89","type":"paragraph","text":"1、广州工人造反派要以“红旗工人”、“工联”、“八一战斗兵团”，“广州工人”为核心首先联合起来。可以分三步联合：⑴基层战斗队的联合。⑵中层分部的联合。⑶各总部的联合。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"dae93cd912","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1b9f75b1b1","type":"paragraph","text":"2、工人造反派联合起来后，马上武装工人，可以武装2─3万人，双方签订的四项协议是靠不住的。","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"dae93cd912","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"45065d0fc1","type":"paragraph","text":"3、总理指出：“春雷”（是铁路系统的老保）已走向反面。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"dae93cd912","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a410a25831","type":"paragraph","text":"4、造反派不要介入他们（公安局）的问题，要依靠他们自己解决。“125”的确是个大杂烩，没有承认自己的错误和缺点，但不要推到保守派那儿去，要团结大多数帮助教育他们。","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"dae93cd912","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"03dc5d4e4f","type":"paragraph","text":"5、总理指出先孤立分化瓦解“地总”、“春雷”、“（毛泽东）主义（红卫）兵”，“工交红旗”、“红旗工人赤卫队”可以争取。","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"dae93cd912","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}